Statue of Libery.name: Statue of Libery
Statue of Libery.effect:
Take this card when you roll at least 3 OUCH.
Gain 3 Victory Points when you take this card.
Lose 3 Victory Points when you lose this card.

Superstar.name: Superstar
Superstar.effect:
Take this card when you roll at least 3 VICTORY. Gain 1 Victory Points, +1 Victory Points per additional VICTORY you rolled.
While you have this card, you gain 1 Victory Points for each VICTORY you roll.
